# Most Used [pandas](https://pandas.pydata.org/?utm_source=chatgpt.com) Functions Cheat Sheet

| Topic               | Function            | Purpose                      |
| ------------------- | ------------------- | ---------------------------- |
| View first rows     | `head()`            | Show first rows              |
| View last rows      | `tail()`            | Show last rows               |
| Shape               | `shape`             | Rows and columns count       |
| Column names        | `columns`           | Show all columns             |
| Data types          | `dtypes`            | Show datatype of columns     |
| Basic info          | `info()`            | Full DataFrame info          |
| Statistics          | `describe()`        | Mean, min, max, etc.         |
| Select columns      | `[[]]`              | Select specific columns      |
| Select row by index | `iloc[]`            | Select rows using index      |
| Select by label     | `loc[]`             | Select rows/columns by label |
| Filtering           | `data[condition]`   | Filter rows                  |
| Sort values         | `sort_values()`     | Sort data                    |
| Unique values       | `unique()`          | Show unique values           |
| Count unique        | `nunique()`         | Count unique values          |
| Value counts        | `value_counts()`    | Count repeated values        |
| Missing values      | `isnull()`          | Detect missing values        |
| Fill missing values | `fillna()`          | Replace NaN                  |
| Remove missing rows | `dropna()`          | Delete NaN rows              |
| Remove columns      | `drop()`            | Delete rows/columns          |
| Rename columns      | `rename()`          | Change column names          |
| Add new column      | `data["new"] =`     | Create column                |
| Apply function      | `apply()`           | Apply custom function        |
| Average             | `mean()`            | Calculate average            |
| Maximum             | `max()`             | Largest value                |
| Minimum             | `min()`             | Smallest value               |
| Sum                 | `sum()`             | Total value                  |
| Count               | `count()`           | Non-null count               |
| Grouping            | `groupby()`         | Group data                   |
| Merge DataFrames    | `merge()`           | Combine tables               |
| Join DataFrames     | `join()`            | Join tables                  |
| Concatenate         | `concat()`          | Combine DataFrames           |
| Remove duplicates   | `drop_duplicates()` | Delete duplicate rows        |
| Check duplicates    | `duplicated()`      | Find duplicates              |
| Convert datatype    | `astype()`          | Change datatype              |
| Read CSV            | `read_csv()`        | Load CSV                     |
| Save CSV            | `to_csv()`          | Save CSV                     |
| Read JSON           | `read_json()`       | Load JSON                    |
| Save JSON           | `to_json()`         | Save JSON                    |
| Read Excel          | `read_excel()`      | Load Excel                   |
| Save Excel          | `to_excel()`        | Save Excel                   |
| Random rows         | `sample()`          | Get random data              |
| Index reset         | `reset_index()`     | Reset row index              |
| Set index           | `set_index()`       | Make column index            |
| Correlation         | `corr()`            | Relationship between columns |
| Replace values      | `replace()`         | Replace values               |
| Query data          | `query()`           | Filter using query string    |

